title: HOUSE ARRYN MARCH TO WAR - Seven Kingdoms Total War Mod Gameplay
description:
Game of Thrones Gameplay - We are back playing the Seven Kingdoms Mod for Total War Attila.  This Time I command House Arryn and I take on House Bolton commanded by Jackiefish!  We wanted to have a massive cavalry/Pike battle!  Enjoy the Battle :D

Jackie's Channel: https://www.youtube.com/user/Jackiefishhhhhh

Moddb: http://www.moddb.com/mods/seven-kingdoms-total-war

Patreon for Mod: https://www.patreon.com/sevenkingdoms


If you enjoyed the video don't forget to Like and Leave a comment :D
